{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then those-- and in that-- during that time we did have a little romance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was 15.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, 14. 15, 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he stayed with me for three days-- everybody went on-- until most of the measles were gone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we went to Munich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we came to Munich I found my Uncle Osher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He survived Dachau, and he was there with my cousin Wolf Prensky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came to Munich, we started to inquire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And found-- and I met some people already who were from Lithuania there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- there was a DP camp there in Munich, and they said, oh, you know, your Uncle Osher is there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- I think, perhaps, one day, because my Uncle Osher also knew somehow that I was coming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he came, picked me up, and, of course, took me to [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Batels. ?] It's a suburb of-- it's-- well, it's a beautiful town in Bavaria, which is about an hour from Munich.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he took me to Bavaria, and I remember that I thought this was a palace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My uncle, again, like in the ghetto, he was always knew how to organize himself, how to do public relations.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was actually distributor-- a manufacturer's distributor before the war, so he had many accounts in-- in-- overseas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he immediately started, when he survived-- when he was liberated, he immediately started writing letters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He has a memory like never ends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To this day, he's alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He lives in Vancouver.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in fact, I'm going to go over there and make a tape of-- of my family, of things-- because he remembers everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
